<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَالنِّيَّةُ شَرْطٌ لِكُلِّ طَهَارَةٍ شَرْعِيَّةٍ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِزَالَةِ خَبَثٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَغُسْلِ كِتَابِيَّةٍ لِحِلِّ وَطْءٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَمُسْلِمَةٍ مُمْتَنِعَةٍ لِذلِكَ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالتَّسْمِيَةُ وَاجِبَةٌ فِي:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
